# Veritabanı & Prisma

PostgreSQL 16. Schema tek kaynak: `apps/api/prisma/schema.prisma` — `Docs/02_DATABASE_SCHEMA.md` ile sync.

## Konvansiyonlar

- Tablo: snake_case plural (`case_transitions`)
- Model: PascalCase (`CaseTransition`)
- Standart alanlar: `id`, `created_at`, `updated_at` (append-only tablolarda update yok)
- Soft delete: yalnızca master data; audit/case_transition append-only

## Encryption Alanları

Hassas kolonlar ciphertext (ByteA/JSONB encrypted). Service katmanında CryptoService encrypt/decrypt — Prisma raw plaintext yazma yasak.

Encrypted örnekler: `incident_description`, `category_specific_data`, `reporter_identity_*`, `reason_text_masked`.

## Migration

- Dev: `prisma migrate dev` · Prod: `prisma migrate deploy` only
- Naming: `YYYYMMDDHHMMSS_kebab_description`
- Her migration PR: rollback/forward plan + sentetik test
- Schema drift CI'da denetlenir

## Transaction Kuralları

Interactive `$transaction` — kısmi commit yasak. Optimistic lock: `optimistic_lock_version` increment.

## Append-Only Tablolar

`audit_logs`, `case_transitions`, `task_events` — DB trigger ile UPDATE/DELETE engeli. Application'da update denemesi yasak.

## Anti-pattern'ler

- Production'da ddl-auto / manuel SQL hotfix
- Migration without doc update (`Docs/02`)
- N+1 query — list endpoint'lerde include/select planla

